data.description: Recently renovated brick home in New Orleans' premier gated golf course community of English Turn.  English Turn is a 650-acre planned community with 24-7 security, 26+ acres of community parks and home to a Jack Nicklaus-designed championship golf course with country club facilities.  This custom brick home has 4 bedrooms and 3 full and one half bath.  Home sits on a homesite of almost 1/3 acre which can be appreciated from a large screened-in patio.  There are hardwood floors in the dining room and front study.  Living room features a fireplace and a wall of windows looking out upon your rear backyard oasis.  All of this and just minutes to the French Quarter and Central Business District.  Seller is offering either up to an allowance of $20,000 for home upgrades or, for qualifying buyers, assumption of a VA mortgage with a 2.25% interest rate.  Two great incentives for a great place to call home!
